column5: Wondering why the fishing is a little slow of late? Head down to your local fishway and don't forget the kid's. http://smg.photobucket.com/albums/v498/chr...nt=MVI_0762.flv
Oh geez, the second fish that jumped took a header right into the concrete wall
That's a really cool video.  Thanks.

Cool video. Growing up my grandparents lived within walking distance of the dam on the Ganny. Every easter it was a family ritual to go for a walk and  "watch the fish jump". Pretty amazing stuff. It was funny how a crowd would gather and cheer em on.

I like standing right where you took that vid from. The ones that jump aren't nearly as impressive as the ones that just power thier way up the flow........without ever leaving the water. Friggen awesome!!  Sinker
Good stuff.  Rainbow amaze me at what they can power through.
